snippet.title: Amber Heard allegedly defecated in Johnny Depp’s bed!?! New AUDIO Released!
snippet.description:
***update🙌🏻 thank you all for the views! I so appreciate the support! Please like and subscribe! Also, share with friends! 

Hi guys, I wanted to make a video on this topic domestic violence. Domestic violence Is horrible no matter who you are and it’s never OK!! I’m going to link the audio below as well as other links related... what’re your thoughts? It’s all pretty disgusting and disturbing!! 

In my opinion,  the audio link below Johnny seems to be stuttering and can’t get a word in edgewise.  Amber just keeps repeating the same thing over and over again without anything new. It doesn’t seem to make sense. He keeps saying “I love you” and she is silent.  

Trigger warning: very disturbing to me.
